data.description: AWESOME HOME IN "PLUMAS LAKE, CA" LOCATED IN A GREAT COMMUNITY WITH GREAT SCHOOLS! This LARGE Single-Story (2,504 SQFT) home has 4 Bedrooms + an Office/Den that functions as a 5TH Bedroom! 3-Car tandem garage for lots of storage! SOLAR HOME! Home has a HUGE RV/Boat/Toy storage area! WOW, you can drive to the backyard from the driveway! The driveway area is big & fits a number of vehicles easily. Home has a very spacious kitchen with an island & nook area. GREAT FLOOR-PLAN! Open concept  living with high ceilings & a spacious feel in each room of the home including the bedrooms. The LOT is HUGE (+/- 0.29 acres) or (+/- 12,600 SQFT lot). The backyard is very useable & also offers privacy. Location is great with easy access to HWYs 70 / 99 / 65 for commuting to Sacramento, Roseville, or Yuba City.  This home has so much to offer. MUST SEE HOME.
